title: Mummy Yummy
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Singaporean
description: Vegetarian stall offers food at cheap prices with dishes like chicken rice, curry rice, char siew rice, lor mee, and curry puff. Has chrysanthemum and herbal tea. Business is involved in delivering free food to needy families. Nov 2015 while the Centre is under renovation the food stall is open.
streetAddress: 62 Sungei Kadut Loop, International Furniture Centre, 03-01
